# CCNA LAB 04 — UplinkFast & BackboneFast in Action

## Objective

Build a Layer 2 redundant topology and observe how classic 802.1D STP converges during indirect and direct link failures.

Test:

* Default STP convergence behavior
* UplinkFast recovery improvement
* BackboneFast indirect failure detection

Measure:

* Packet loss duration
* Port state transitions
* Recovery time improvement

This lab demonstrates why Cisco introduced STP enhancement features before RSTP existed.

