# STEP 1 — BASIC CONFIGURATION

## DSW1

# Configure root bridge

```cisco id="q38g74"
enable
configure terminal

hostname DSW1
no ip domain-lookup

spanning-tree mode pvst

vlan 10
 name USERS

spanning-tree vlan 10 root primary

interface range g0/1 - 2
 switchport trunk encapsulation dot1q
 switchport mode trunk

end
write memory
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

